-
-Implements _bin_pack_layout using best-fit decreasing (BFD) algorithm:
-- Sorts tiles by area descending
-- Places each tile in the best-fit existing row or starts a new row
-- Maintains 2px spacing between tiles
-- Raises SurfaceAssemblyError on overflow
-
-Adds BinPackLayoutTest with 7 tests covering empty tiles, single tile, side-by-side placement, varying sizes, spacing, overflow error, and known layout.
-
-Updates assemble_ui_sheet to use _bin_pack_layout instead of naive row-wrap."
